annotationA: Autophagy-related protein 3; Small conjugating protein ligase activity; Atg8 ligase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: autophagy
annotationB: Autophagy-related protein 9; Involved in autophagy and cytoplasm to vacuole transport (Cvt) vesicle formation. Plays a key role in the organization of the preautophagosomal structure/phagophore assembly site (PAS), the nucleating site for formation of the sequestering vesicle
